Package: estDLVM
Type: Package
Title: Discrete latent variable models estimation through different versions of the EM algorithm
Version: 1.0
Date: 2022-08-22
Authors@R: c(
  person("Luca", "Brusa", email = "luca.brusa@unimib.it", role = c("cre", "aut")))
Description: The estDLVM package provides functions to perform maximum likelihood estimation in the field of discrete latent variable models. Three different variants of the Expectation-Maximization algorithm are implemented (standard, tempered, and evolutionary), and many models are taken into account (Latent Class, Hidden Markov, and Stochastic Block models).
License: GPL-3
Imports: 
  Rcpp (>= 1.0.8),
  RcppParallel (>= 5.1.5), 
  RcppArmadillo (>= 0.11.0), 
  RcppAlgos (>= 2.5.3), 
  ppclust (>= 1.1.0),
  phonTools
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, RcppParallel
SystemRequirements: GNU make
